  <div id="whatwedo" class="section">
    <h2>Here's what we do</h2>
    <p>We craft meaningful digital experiences rooted in empathy, clarity, and cultural depth. From UX strategy to interface design, we help mission-driven startups and visionary orgs design products that feel as good as they function.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="howwedo" class="section">
    <h2>Here's how we do it</h2>
    <p>We blend sharp research with soulful thinking. Through collaborative sprints, rapid prototyping, and story-led design, we solve real problems for real people—without losing the magic. Our process is transparent, iterative, and always human-first.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="whoweworkwith" class="section">
    <h2>Who We Work With</h2>
    <p>We collaborate with founders, teams, and organizations who care deeply about the people they’re building for. Whether you're an early-stage startup shaping a product from scratch, or an established company looking to rethink your UX, if you believe design should respect—not just impress—we’re listening.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="philosophy" class="section">
    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>We believe design isn’t decoration... it’s dignity. That good UX is invisible, but unforgettable. That the future should feel human, not just look sleek. And that every interaction, from a button to a story, holds the power to connect, comfort, or change someone’s day.</p>
  </div>
  
